<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 16:48:16 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a2ae6ce1dfb0</link><description>&lt;p&gt;您好，请提供您需要翻译的英文段落。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A path through a dense green hedge. East Modernist facade in the back, and a bright sunlit walkway crossing in front." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a2ae6ce1dfb0.jpg" width="1128"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 16:48:16 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a2ade1702542</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今天我沿着风景优美的路线去了另一个村庄，途中经过了这座小教堂。它始建于13世纪20年代，位于从奥斯陆到特隆赫姆的一条朝圣路线上。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A small Romanesque-style church made of brick and black wooden roofs with a tiny bell tower in the middle of the main nave. It stands on a small hill surrounded by grass and trees. The sky is blue with just one small cotton cloud." height="2934" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a2ade1702542.jpg" width="3000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 16:11:06 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a2a8eb8b6812</link><description>&lt;p&gt;请提供完整的英文内容，以便我进行准确翻译。您目前只输入了“Sl”，这似乎不完整。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Sl" height="7728" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/pmurad/6a2a8eb8b6812.jpg" width="5152"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://pmurad.some.pics"&gt;@pmurad&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 10:32:29 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>自行车通勤</title><link>https://some.pics/6a2a65d7a30b4</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🚲 通勤&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="🚲 Commute" height="3913" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/atog/6a2a65d7a30b4.jpg" width="2930"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://atog.some.pics"&gt;@atog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 07:38:03 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>圆形大厅</title><link>https://some.pics/6a29f6b3e2a8c</link><description>&lt;p&gt;圆形大厅&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A high stucco and wood rotunda with frosted glass." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/6a29f6b3e2a8c.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 23:43:52 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>